summary: This document is an email from September 20, 2019, regarding technical issues encountered while uploading files to an 'Epstein shared' location. The sender reports that 46 files failed to copy, appearing damaged or corrupted, and suggests IT intervention.

events.title: File upload issue to Epstein shared location
events.description: An email was sent reporting that 46 files failed to copy to the 'Epstein shared' location, with files appearing damaged, corrupted, or too large.

keyFacts: The email references an 'Epstein shared' location, indicating a shared storage or collaboration space related to Epstein.
46 files failed to copy during an upload attempt, with errors suggesting file corruption or size issues.
The email suggests IT involvement to resolve the technical problems with the files.
